Class Book

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.booker.Book
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Book
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Book class for storing data and metadata of books. Firestore can insert the data from a book document directly into one of these.
